text: The Pays-d'Enhaut District was a district of the canton of Vaud, Switzerland. The seat of the district was the municipality of Château-d'Œx. As of 2006 it is part of the Riviera-Pays-d'Enhaut District. * Cercle de Château-d'Œx ** Château-d'Œx * Cercle de Rougemont ** Rossinière ** Rougemont Category:Former districts of Vaud
